5000|$|Block: The block driver allows using raw Linux block devices as backstores {{for export}} via LIO. This {{includes}} physical devices, such as HDDs, SSDs, CDs/DVDs, <b>RAM</b> <b>disks,</b> etc., and logical devices, such as software or hardware RAID volumes or LVM volumes.|$|R
